                <h1><a>Inductive biases of neural network modularity in spatial navigation</a></h1>

                <div class="post-info">
                    <div class="post-authors">
                    <h4>Authors</h4>
                    <a href="https://blog.ml.cmu.edu/author/ruiyiz/" title="Posts by Ruiyi Zhang" class="author url fn" rel="author">Ruiyi Zhang</a>                    </div>
